{"tid":1562125,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"羅范想說甚麼 - 曾志豪","createTime":"2019-09-12T01:39:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T01:47:52.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dc44687672614dfa6f0c5309a70ef5aef85bbad3","tid":1562125,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T01:39:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9B%BE%E5%BF%97%E8%B1%AA/daily/article/20190912/20766422\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259B%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E8%25B1%25AA%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190912%2F20766422&d=duP9xtlDTMOxgFFwFRXy%2FakErG%2BwP2VMcW32eObqVUU%3D&h=266e4322\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259B%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E8%25B1%25AA%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190912%2F20766422&h=2ec83ff3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9B%BE%E5%BF%97%E8%B1%AA/daily/article/20190912/20766422</a><br />\n<br />\n羅范想說甚麼 - 曾志豪<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20190912/large/1568193936_c009.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20190912%2Flarge%2F1568193936_c009.jpg&h=d3aebaa9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港電台圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n羅范的「免費性愛論」迅速成為全城笑話，大家終於領略「人一藍、腦便殘」的真理。<br />\n<br />\n羅范卻又同時打破了世俗對藍絲的看法，一般都以為藍絲特徵是：年老（佢中咗）、低學歷（佢係高學歷低人格）、低收入（佢嘅收入應該同智商成反比），其實不然。仗義每多屠狗輩，許多罵走黑警的忠義街坊可能來自公屋，而高學歷高收入但跌咗個良心的也大有人在（佢又中咗）。<br />\n<br />\n為何羅范要把這些道聽塗說的流言當成真話？第一，她故意抹黑。第二，她真心膠相信，而我覺得後者機會很大。畢竟她和她的姐妹，同為行會成員的乜太，連「Air Drop、連登」都覺得是軍事高科技涉及境外勢力支援，這樣的視野，又豈能分辨出新聞的真偽呢？<br />\n<br />\n可是抹黑的機會，故意擾亂敵人的機會更高。<br />\n<br />\n因為這場仗，從一開始，便是「誰大誰惡誰正確」的配對遊戲。誰大？政府囉。誰惡？黑警囉。誰正確？抗爭者囉。<br />\n<br />\n抗爭者在這場運動中，得到一致好評，站在道德高地，有強大的道德感召力，在黑警和暴政的對面堅守陣地。<br />\n<br />\n特別是年輕人，一個一個的「不畏懼不徇私不對他人懷惡意」&hellip;&hellip;Sorry，搞錯咗對象，所以你有黑警扑頭，那邊有街坊夾道歡呼抗爭者凱旋而歸。<br />\n<br />\n政權雖然天天打人，但輿論上，處於捱打狀態。<br />\n<br />\n所以政權一直很想抹黑抗爭運動，最早期便把抗爭者的「不怕死」抹黑為「收咗錢出嚟遊行有安家費」。因為政權無法解釋，為何會有這許多有用的之軀投身遊行示威，總不能承認香港人已經頂自己唔順嗎？<br />\n<br />\n「收錢論」不成功，因為太荒謬，於是再下一計，便是羅范這種「免費性愛服務」的「抹黃」言論。<br />\n<br />\n因為政權解釋不了，為何整整一代的年輕人，大學生中學生甚至小學生，都在抗爭陣營，為何沒有義士願意撐警撐政府？<br />\n<br />\n所以政權愈是抹黑抹黃，便愈是代表政權害怕人民，害怕這些高潔的靈魂，號召更多人民加入。羅范想說，政權真的害怕了。 <br />\n<br />\n曾志豪<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n伸縮警棍 (尊子)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n銀幕黑警 (邁克)"},{"pid":"4a4cbac0d956260f079508056d1522258ff95b10","tid":1562125,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T01:40:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"00bd8416d5e53fb663c3e8529cf14afd9fe47f56","tid":1562125,"uid":58958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T01:40:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>叫阿爺阿嫲阿公阿婆阿爸阿媽投</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=